Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:42.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:100997,102040}What's that, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.66,0:01:44.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:102665,104125}You can do better!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.29,0:01:48.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:105293,108379}Go faster!\NLassie's gonna get ahead of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:50.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:109005,110173}Told you…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:51.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111007,111883}I'm at my limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:04.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:121768,124020}Lassie's so far already…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:30.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148795,150296}What's up, Toots?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:35.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152965,155176}Oh, who do we have here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:38.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157512,158429}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:39.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:158429,159639}Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:41.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159639,161766}Are you the owner\Nof this big fellow?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:43.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:162016,163309}I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:44.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:163309,164268}Who are you, mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:50.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:166437,170066}I reached an intersection\Nand wondered which way to go…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:51.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170066,171275}So much that I fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:02:59.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:178074,179200}All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:01.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179200,181202}Time to introduce ourselves\Nto our new audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:02.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:181744,182745}Audience?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:05.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:182745,185206}We're not your audience… I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:07.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185957,187792}I'm sorry to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:08.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187792,188710}Right, Toots?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:13.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191421,193089}Oh, my goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:16.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193089,196509}Toots is so sad,\Nhis heart is about to break!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:19.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196509,199846}Quick, someone come here\Nand ease his grief!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:37.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216612,217739}Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:40.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:219490,220450}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:49.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:227457,229417}This guy is my partner.\NName's Toots.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:52.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:230126,232420}And over there\Nis my other partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:55.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233045,235923}Her name is Beth.\NHer specialty is pulling the carriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:03:59.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:237133,239218}That leaves me. I'm Rolly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:01.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:239218,241846}By the way, how good\Nis the bakery in your town?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:03.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241846,243806}Bakery? I guess it's pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:06.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243806,246392}Are you serious?\NMr. Rice's bakery is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:07.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246392,247143}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:08.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:247143,248144}That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:11.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:248144,251272}He's helped by his daughter Mary,\Nthe prettiest girl in the whole town!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:12.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:251272,252607}All right, it's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:14.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:252607,254609}I've decided where\NI'm going today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:15.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254609,255735}Ain't that right, Toots?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:24.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263618,264827}Finally it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:27.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:264827,267038}Let's go for a drink tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:33.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271083,273336}Oh? You're still busy with\Nthe deliveries at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:36.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273503,276422}You work harder than we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:49.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287725,289560}John? Sandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:51.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289560,291521}Lassie, too?\NWhat are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:11.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309705,311791}Isn't that amazing, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:13.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:311791,313209}Wanna try it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:23.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:322343,323636}And for the next show…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:27.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:324136,327098}We're going to have\None of you lend a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:28.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:327098,328140}Let's see…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:31.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328558,331602}How about that pretty lady over there?\NThink you can do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:34.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:333312,334397}Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:37.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334397,337024}Who else could I have in mind\Nwhen I called for a "pretty lady"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:38.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337024,338150}Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:42.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340987,342655}Here, please hold this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:45.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344365,345324}Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:46.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:345324,346784}Perfect. You're skilled at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:47.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346784,347952}Go, Toots.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:06:00.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356669,360298}Ladies and gentlemen,\Nthat was my partner, Toots,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:02.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360298,362758}and this cute miss.\NLet's have a round of applause for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:09.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365887,369265}And now, ladies and gentlemen,\NI invite you to take a look at my stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:11.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369265,371893}We sell all sorts of\Ncooking utensils and pans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:13.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:372184,373936}Let's go, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:20.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379191,380776}Good doggie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:23.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381903,383738}Thank you for your purchase.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:25.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383738,385323}– I'd like this one.\N– Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:28.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385448,388993}Rolly is doing business\Nwhile traveling all around England.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:30.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388993,390828}I wish I could go\Nto many places like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:31.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:390828,391412}Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:33.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391412,393372}Oh, I forgot, I forgot, I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:35.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393372,395666}I've almost forgotten\Nthe most important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:37.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395666,397126}Can you buy me some bread?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:38.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397126,398628}Sure. Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:41.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:400338,401672}Let's go.\NWe're going to the bakery.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:43.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401672,403549}Hey, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:46.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403966,406510}How can you leave\Nyour stand like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:52.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409430,412391}I am so sorry, but we're\Nsold out of the bread for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:54.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412391,414602}– Not even one?\N– Unfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:57.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414977,417730}We'll have a new batch\Nready for tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:06:59.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418064,419982}I understand…\NThat's a bit of a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:01.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419982,421525}You don't have bread for tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:02.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421525,422401}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422401,424487}It's not for us.\NIt's for Rolly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:05.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424487,425613}Rolly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:08.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425613,428240}Ah, that man\Nwith the acrobatic puppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:10.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428240,430701}The cheers were so loud we could\Nhear them all the way down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:14.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:430701,434455}He came to our town because I told him\Nthat we have a great bakery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.45,0:07:15.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:434455,435081}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:15.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435081,435998}Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:17.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435998,437375}There's nothing to sell anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:18.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437375,438876}Come here and help me\Naround the stove.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:19.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:438876,439877}Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:22.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:439877,442922}Tell me, is he going\Nto stay here overnight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:23.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442922,443881}Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:26.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443881,446842}Tell him to come here tomorrow morning.\NWe'll give him a nice fresh bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:27.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446842,447385}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:30.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:449971,450846}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.84,0:07:32.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:450846,452556}That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:37.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:453057,457520}Soft and fresh bread is a delight\Nto the taste buds and the soul alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:39.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457520,459855}Besides, there's the beautiful girl\Nyou told me about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:42.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:459855,462441}Very well.\NI'll stay here till tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:43.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:462441,463776}But what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:45.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463776,465569}You have nowhere to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:48.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:465945,468572}It's likely nothing to be proud of,\Nbut I don't have a house at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:51.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469365,471450}So, like what? You're\Nsleeping in the stables?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:53.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471617,473703}No, nothing of the sort.\NI'm a vagabond.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:55.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:473703,475329}And it's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:57.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475329,477248}I sleep under\Na beautiful starry sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:08:00.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:477748,480334}Above us is the Milky Way,\Na brilliant path made of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:02.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480334,482336}And I sleep right under it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:03.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:482336,483963}Ain't that right, Toots?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:06.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:485089,486716}The starry sky, huh…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:494724,496642}They look like they're\Nabout to fall down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:18.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496642,498519}That's kind of scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:19.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498519,499270}Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:23.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500438,503065}You must have traveled\Nto many places.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:24.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:503065,504275}You mean me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504608,506277}I guess. Right, Toots?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:33.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507820,513284}Manchester, Glasgow, Newcastle,\Nand also Liverpool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:38.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:514744,518247}But no matter where I went,\NI went to nameless towns and villages only.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:43.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:520124,523169}I like places like these the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:46.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524086,526797}For example, even if\NI sleep outdoors tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:52.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:526797,532261}I feel relieved as I'm surrounded\Nby houses with people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:56.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:532553,536932}Behind every dimly lit window\Nthere is a happy family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:09:03.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:537516,543064}When I think of it,\NI get this warm and gentle feeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:05.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543064,545191}and I feel like I'm home myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:10.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546442,550696}But Mr. Rice is very short-tempered\Nand always yells at everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:14.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551739,554825}No, no.\NYou shouldn't say such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:16.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554825,556702}He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:19.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559038,559830}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:22.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:560915,562124}It's Sandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:31.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:569423,571759}I see you too have a nose\Nfor delicious things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:42.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580101,582103}I'm telling you, Beth.\NThis tastes amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:44.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583145,584271}Really-really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:46.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:584688,586565}Really-really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:49.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:587149,589777}But I need to say,\Nthis is one venerable old pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:53.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591028,593280}It'll serve for many years\Nif it gets patched up a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:57.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594156,597284}Your mother keeps\Nher dishes very well, Sandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:09:58.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597701,598327}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:09:59.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598327,599787}But that pot is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:03.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:600830,603290}I got it from my late grandma\Nwhen I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:05.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603290,605251}I took care of it the best I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:08.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605251,608754}So, the one who made\Nthis delicious soup was…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:09.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:608754,609547}Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:13.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:610881,613259}I see. Forgive me my insolence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:16.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:613259,616804}Well, now you know.\NRight, Toots?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:21.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620141,621976}How are things over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:24.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:621976,624478}Have you seen any shooting stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:25.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624478,625312}Not really…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:27.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626397,627106}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:28.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627690,628899}There is one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:31.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628899,631110}Eh? Where?\NWhere, where?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.11,0:10:32.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:631110,632236}It's gone already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:33.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632236,633571}I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:36.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633571,636907}I really saw it!\NA shooting star… Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:45.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644373,645249}Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:48.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645958,648419}Making a campfire\Nin a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:51.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:648419,651255}What if it gets out of control?\NFor crying out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:54.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:652047,654008}All right, kids, time for you\Nto go to your homes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.00,0:10:55.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654008,655885}But we're having so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:11:00.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656760,660764}Each of you has a warm house with\Ntheir mom and dad waiting for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:05.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:660764,665394}If you play for too long in the evenings,\Nyou'll end up homeless like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:07.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:665936,667396}See you tomorrow, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:09.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:667396,669899}Will you do a show\Ntomorrow again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:14.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:672234,674486}Toots says he'd like\Nto show you some more tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:16.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675029,676447}– Bye!\N– Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:17.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:676447,677406}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:18.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:677406,678991}Let's go, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:25.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681994,685497}Looks like that big fellow\Ntook a liking in you, Toots.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:26.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:686207,686957}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:48.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:707394,708938}All done, Toots.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:49.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708938,709980}Let's go to sleep.
Comment: 0,0:11:58.11,0:11:58.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:718113,718113}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:45.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:763993,765077}Oh my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:52.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:771375,772626}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:55.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:774420,775504}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:57.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:775879,777464}It's fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:12:59.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:777464,779508}Everyone! It's fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:01.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:779508,781802}Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:05.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:783929,785931}Oh? What about the fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:07.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785931,787808}Oh, it's near my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:11.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789435,791562}Water… We need water! Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:16.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:795649,796567}Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:28.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:807077,808329}This looks serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:35.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814335,815127}Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:38.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817171,818088}Sandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:39.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:818088,819840}I'm here with the milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:41.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:820341,821467}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:43.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821467,823344}Oh? But we have\Nenough milk, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:47.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:824303,827473}This time it's\Nfor someone else, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:51.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:827473,831060}Listen, Rolly will appreciate some milk\Nto go with the bread, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:52.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:831060,832394}Ah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:56.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:834021,836940}You want to meet Toots\Nas well, don't you, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:01.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:838776,841111}Who could it be\Nso early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:02.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:841945,842946}– Colin?\N– John!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:04.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:842946,844239}Something bad happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:07.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844239,847618}Rolly… Rolly is in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:08.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:847618,848869}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:24.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:863050,864635}How many times\Ndo I need to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:27.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:864635,867221}I put out the campfire\Nbefore I went to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:29.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:867221,869390}So where did that fire\Ncome from, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:31.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:869390,871517}Let's stay calm, Mr. Rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:34.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:872142,874978}This man worked hard\Nto extinguish the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:36.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:874978,876855}Thanks to him the fire\Ndidn't reach the houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:40.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:876855,880234}So because he extinguished the fire\Nhe himself had started, it's all good?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:43.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880234,883237}Besides, he came out of nowhere\Nsupposedly to sell some pots and pans.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:45.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:883237,885406}Don't think we will\Nlet you off the hook like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:47.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:885406,887241}Hey, hey…\NWhat do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.69,0:14:48.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:887699,888826}Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:51.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888826,891245}Father, you always told me that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:54.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891245,894373}...we should treat every customer who\Ncomes to buy our bread well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:55.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894373,895707}This man is our—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:15:00.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895707,900170}You've got to be kidding me. I make bread\Nfor the people of our town first and foremost.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:03.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:900170,903424}I don't sell to…\Nto nefarious individuals like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:05.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:904258,905175}Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:06.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:905175,906260}You agree with me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:09.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906260,909596}I don't know about your bread, but\Nstarting fire is inexcusable, accident or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:14.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:909930,914101}There you have it. We need to protect\Nthe lives of the people in our town.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:17.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:915018,917980}We're going to have to ask you\Nto leave our town immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:19.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:917980,919231}Any objections?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:24.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:921650,924278}I'm going to tell this once more.\NI didn't set the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:27.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924278,927281}Nope, there's no doubt it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:30.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:927281,930993}Listen. We're doing you a favor,\Nas we didn't involve the police yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:32.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:930993,932119}But you must leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.11,0:15:34.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:932119,934913}I see that much.\NLooks like there's no talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:37.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:936331,937416}See? I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:43.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941378,943172}I'd like you\Nto understand one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:48.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944840,948510}I sell pots and kettles,\Nbecause I have to eat something, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.51,0:15:53.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:948510,953932}But the reason I travel is because I like\Nto make people smile with Toots' acrobatics.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:54.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:953932,954892}Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:00.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:959271,960355}Rolly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:02.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:961148,962149}Are you leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:04.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962149,964026}I have no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:05.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:964443,965611}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.61,0:16:07.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965611,967529}No "buts".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:09.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968113,969406}Thank you for the soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:10.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969406,970908}It was delightful, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:15.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:973702,975162}It's fixed…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:19.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:975162,979791}The bakery owner wants me to leave\Nto protect the village… Oh, the irony.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:22.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980751,982794}Let's meet again some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:35.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994765,995724}Rolly…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:36.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:995724,996767}He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:41.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:998769,1001480}I don't know if it was\Nthe lamp or something else,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:44.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001480,1004191}but it was so close to our house\Nthat it almost burned because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:44.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004191,1004942}Father…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:46.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005567,1006443}A lamp?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:47.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006985,1007986}Something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:49.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007986,1009071}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:51.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010322,1011532}What's the big idea, Colin?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:53.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011532,1013534}Just do what I asked, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:55.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014117,1015786}So I just knock on that door?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:56.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015786,1016537}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:00.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019164,1020916}J-John, what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:01.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020916,1021917}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:05.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021917,1025045}You need to ask?\NMr. Rice is so scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:06.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025045,1026547}That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:08.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026547,1028340}Excuse me, Mr. Rice…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:10.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028340,1030884}What? If you are here for the bread,\Nwe are not ready yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:13.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030884,1033971}Because of the fire,\Nthe oven has cooled down by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:15.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033971,1035222}It'll take some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:17.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035222,1037266}Quick, he's going away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:19.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037266,1039101}Excuse me, Mr. Rice…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:21.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039726,1041353}What? I'm busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:23.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041353,1043397}Colin wants to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:26.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043772,1046149}Uh, well, it's…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:27.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046441,1047651}Spit it out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:31.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050612,1051947}You tell him, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:37.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055951,1057369}You're for real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:38.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057369,1058161}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:40.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059371,1060455}Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:43.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060747,1063750}Both lamp and the campfire\Nwere put out before 11 o'clock?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:44.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063959,1064626}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:45.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064835,1065586}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:49.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065586,1069298}At any rate, we have a witness. Colin was\Nlooking through the window and saw it clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:51.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069298,1071466}Why a child would stay up\Nuntil so late at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:52.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071466,1072342}Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:55.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072342,1075262}I was trying to see the meteors…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:56.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075262,1076555}Which is why…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:17:58.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076555,1078181}What do you mean, meteors?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:18:01.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078181,1081226}If you raise your voice,\Nyou will scare the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:05.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082144,1085480}Either way, Mr. Rolly\Nput out the lamp
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:08.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085480,1088609}and extinguished the campfire\Nwith water from a pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:09.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088609,1089568}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:10.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089568,1090360}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:13.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090360,1093322}That means the fire must've been\Ncaused by something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:14.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093322,1094072}True.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:18.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094740,1098076}If it was caused by\Nsomething else, that means…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:37.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116011,1117804}Enough, just hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:41.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119473,1121350}Can't you go any faster?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:43.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121350,1123310}Don't distract me\Nwhile I'm driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.47,0:18:47.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124478,1127856}But still, what should I\Nsay to that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:49.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127856,1129316}Apologize to him, naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.77,0:18:53.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129775,1133236}But I only thought of the safety\Nof the people of our town.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:54.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133236,1134821}He ought to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:58.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134821,1138825}Don't make excuses, Father.\NJust admit that we were at fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:03.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139534,1143080}I had so much fun with Rolly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.08,0:19:03.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143080,1143538}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:07.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144164,1147250}What if we turn into a town\Nthat nobody wants to come to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:08.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147250,1148543}That would be a bummer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:13.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149002,1153548}I wanted to talk\Nto Mr. Rolly a lot more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:25.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163016,1165811}Why the long face, Toots?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:28.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165811,1168772}People should just laugh it off\Nin such an event.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.77,0:19:30.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168772,1170982}Oh, but you're a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:52.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190377,1192170}What's wrong, Beth?\NWhy have you stopped?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:56.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194256,1196675}Hey, hurry up, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:58.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196675,1198635}A ship is going\Nto come here any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.68,0:20:09.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206685,1209229}There he is!\NIt's Rolly's carriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:10.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209229,1210605}Ah! But…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:14.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212399,1214860}Rolly is going to cross the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:17.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214860,1217028}Damn, the engine is done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:22.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221450,1222576}Rolly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:24.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222576,1224119}Wait for us, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.03,0:20:30.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228039,1230667}You too, Father.\NLet's run with the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:35.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234129,1235922}What's wrong, Beth?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:40.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236631,1240510}I'd like to cross the bridge\Nand leave things behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:43.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240510,1243930}I can't wait to meet\Nthe people in the next town.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.22,0:20:52.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1251229,1252606}Come on, Beth!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.69,0:20:58.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1257694,1258737}Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:21:00.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1258737,1260197}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:01.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1260197,1261448}Toots!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:05.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1264868,1265827}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.82,0:21:07.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1265827,1267954}Don't cross the bridge, Rolly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:10.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268455,1270582}My father…\NMy father wants you to stay, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:12.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1270749,1272584}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:14.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1272584,1274252}Don't go anywhere yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:36.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1292938,1296441}I see, so these children\Nhave proven my innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:40.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1296441,1300529}This is why the world is such an interesting\Nplace to live in. Ain't that right, Toots?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:44.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1303406,1304741}I see, I see!
